author: cutting
msg: Fix HADOOP-67.  Add a public API for dfs statistics.  Also switch to use the public API for reporting in DFSShell.

author: steveh
msg: Changed references to "Callback" to "Method" in the samples and webapp-template.  I've restricted the changes to the user-facing files.

author: rahul
msg: All logs are now private, with getters and setters where subclassing may be anticipated.

author: dain
msg: Marked all ObjectName kernel methods as deprecated
Replaced use of GBeanQuery with AbstractNameQuery
Replaced unnecessary proxy creation with calls to kernel.getGBean
Improved NO_PROXY flag to cause reflective kernel invocations to not use CGLib fast class
Removed properties from environment object as they are no longer used anywhere

author: jukka
msg: JCR-379: Removed the unnecessary cqfs dependency.
JCR-378: The slf4j-log4f12 dependency was in fact already included, just not bundled in the war. Use that previous dependency.
